HEADWORD: Pistache
<hw>Pis*tache"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[OE.
<ets>pistace</ets>, fr. F. <ets>pistache</ets>. See
<er>Pistachio</er>.]</ety> <fld>(Bot.)</fld> <def>The anacardiaceous
